                    "text": "MYLES CRAWFORD: _(His cock's wattles wagging)_ Hello, seventyseven eightfour. Hello. _Freeman's Urinal_ and _Weekly Arsewipe_ here. Paralyse Europe. You which? Bluebags? Who writes? Is it Bloom?"
