                    "chapter": 2,
                    "para": 4312,
                    "text": "BEAUFOY: _(His lip upcurled, smiles superciliously on the court)_ You funny ass, you! You're too beastly awfully weird for words! I don't think you need over excessively disincommodate yourself in that regard. My literary agent Mr J. B. Pinker is in attendance. I presume, my lord, we shall receive the usual witnesses' fees, shan't we? We are considerably out of pocket over this bally pressman johnny, this jackdaw of Rheims, who has not even been to a university."
