                    "text": "BLOOM: _(Uncloaks impressively, revealing obesity, unrolls a paper and reads solemnly)_ Aleph Beth Ghimel Daleth Hagadah Tephilim Kosher Yom Kippur Hanukah Roschaschana Beni Brith Bar Mitzvah Mazzoth Askenazim Meshuggah Talith."
