                    "text": "EDWARD THE SEVENTH: _(Slowly, solemnly but indistinctly)_ Peace, perfect peace. For identification, bucket in my hand. Cheerio, boys. _(He turns to his subjects)_ We have come here to witness a clean straight fight and we heartily wish both men the best of good luck. Mahak makar a bak."
